{"tid":1565113,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[文宣]你班連登仔真係以為好多人上連登？","createTime":"2019-09-13T04:30:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-13T04:39:00.000Z","uid":287384,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"7c06c0e808bf0f20f9681cbac39700012a3de71a","tid":1565113,"uid":287384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T04:30:59.000Z","msg":"有冇諗過仲有好多<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n中坑 銀髮族<br />\n係<span style=\"color: red;\">唔上連登<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n靠睇連儂牆 收wtsapp</span><br />\n嚟接近抗爭資訊㗎？</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Cd5Nmod.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCd5Nmod.png&h=2067c22d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我知大家最近睇到嘔<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">但好多街坊都未睇呀</span><br />\n點解？<br />\n因為依家好多連儂牆都<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">冇人文宣</span>呀<br />\n有d牆仲係癡住8月5三罷呀<br />\n<br />\n仲要依家多左好多獅子狗呀<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">說好既<span style=\"color: red;\">撕一貼十</span>呢？？？</span><br />\n依家對面幫我哋清左咁多空位<br />\n大家唔係唔做嘢呀？<br />\n<br />\n今晚中秋 咁多手足<br />\n唔使驚畀廢老搞<br />\n全部人除左食燈籠玩月餅 <br />\n唱歌尻叫玩激光之餘<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">去埋連儂牆做文宣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2tuZcCM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2tuZcCM.jpg&h=2ce4061a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/59irB4t.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F59irB4t.jpg&h=281a1d44&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dz6T1wa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fdz6T1wa.jpg&h=7ca57435&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港<br />\n時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"4a8fd565d5488c20c7586f7de6a57d5a2f9